“I built a fully responsive portfolio using modular HTML structure, a CSS design system with variables, and JavaScript for interactivity. I integrated EmailJS for contact functionality, ScrollReveal for animations, and implemented features like dynamic navigation highlighting, a modal system, and typed text animation to enhance user experience.”


